channel.title: I need Help With RSMV :(
channel.description:
Okay, I was folowing CJ's RSMV Guide, and while my RSMV was downloading the Cache, it stopped at 32997. I kept trying but the same thing happened every time. I just wanna know what im doing wrong :( This is what it keeps saying...
[code]C:\Documents and Settings\Owner\Desktop\RSMV>java Main Grabbing cache version. Trying: 543 Accepted Sending Request for model : 32997 Model Grabbing Complete C:\Documents and Settings\Owner\Desktop\RSMV>pause press any key to continue.........[/code]
If you can help in ANY way PLEASE do. (btw, Frell is the one who told me to put this topic in here)
